data.title: Wedding Ceremony
data.description: Tim & Kirsten exchange vows on the Garden Terrace Lawn
data.dress_code: Dapper/Cocktail: Suits, dress chinos, button up shirt and optional tie. We love a pocket kerchief! Classy dress, pantsuit or jumpsuit.
data.notes: Arrive at 2:30 PM for a 3:00 PM start. Ceremony on the Garden Terrace Lawn.

data.title: Wedding Reception
data.description: Join us for dinner, dancing, and celebration! Reception to conclude at 12:00 AM.
data.dress_code: Dapper/Cocktail: Suits, dress chinos, button up shirt and optional tie. We love a pocket kerchief! Classy dress, pantsuit or jumpsuit.
data.notes: Cocktail hour after ceremony followed by reception. Top-shelf bevies, good tunes, and more love than you can poke a stick at!

data.title: Pre-Wedding Drinks
data.description: Tim and Kirsten will be at the Prince of Mereweather pub. Stop in to have a drink and grab yourself a meal if you are hungry.
data.notes: Saturday 4th October, 4-8 PM. Casual drinks and food available.

data.title: Recovery Beach Day
data.description: While we do not have a formal recovery breakfast planned, we will be at Newcastle Beach from 11 am onwards. There is a kiosk that serves good coffee and excellent food. Good for soaking up the libations!
data.notes: Monday October 6th from 11 AM onwards. Kiosk available for coffee and food.
